    "category": "Hardware",
    "description": "<table id=\"settings\" class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\">\n                        <thead>\n                        <tr>\n                            <th style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Problem Statement ID</th>\n                            <td>\n                                <div class=\"style-2\" style=\"overflow-y: auto; min-height:20px; max-height: 200px; width:100%;\"> 25247</div>\n                               </td>\n                            </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                            <th style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Problem Statement Title</th>\n                            <td>\n                                <div class=\"style-2\" style=\"overflow-y: auto; min-height:20px; max-height: 200px; width:100%;\"> Sign Language Capture and Illustration System with Sensor Integration</div>\n                               </td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                            <th style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Description</th>\n                            <td>\n                                <!-- <div class=\"style-2\" style=\"overflow-y: auto; min-height:20px; max-height: 200px; width:100%;\"> &lt;b&gt;Abstract / Problem Statement&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Millions of individuals with speech or hearing impairments rely on sign language for communication, yet a large portion of the population does not understand it, creating barriers in education, workplaces, healthcare, and daily life. The solution aims to bridge this gap by capturing sign language gestures using sensors and translating them into text or speech in real-time. Additionally, the system will illustrate or visualize the recognized gestures to aid in learning and understanding.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Objectives&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Develop a sensor-based wearable glove/device that captures hand and finger movements.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Build a gesture recognition system using ML to detect sign language in real time.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Translate signs into text and/or speech instantly.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Provide visual illustrations of each gesture for learning and verification.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Support Indian Sign Language (ISL) and potentially other languages.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ensure portability, accuracy, and low latency for real-time interaction.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Expected Outcomes&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Working prototype glove and software system.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Accurate sign-to-text/speech conversion (goal: &gt;90% accuracy).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Real-time visual feedback with gesture illustrations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mobile app/web interface for usability.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Deliverables&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Functional prototype of the sensor glove&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Working software application (web/mobile)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ML model with documentation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Codebase (GitHub/GitLab)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Video demo&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Project report and presentation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</div> -->\n                                 <div class=\"style-2\" style=\"overflow-y: auto; min-height:20px; max-height: 200px; width:100%;\"> <b>Abstract / Problem Statement</b><br>Millions of individuals with speech or hearing impairments rely on sign language for communication, yet a large portion of the population does not understand it, creating barriers in education, workplaces, healthcare, and daily life. The solution aims to bridge this gap by capturing sign language gestures using sensors and translating them into text or speech in real-time. Additionally, the system will illustrate or visualize the recognized gestures to aid in learning and understanding.<br><br><b>Objectives</b><br><ul><li>Develop a sensor-based wearable glove/device that captures hand and finger movements.</li><li>Build a gesture recognition system using ML to detect sign language in real time.</li><li>Translate signs into text and/or speech instantly.</li><li>Provide visual illustrations of each gesture for learning and verification.</li><li>Support Indian Sign Language (ISL) and potentially other languages.</li><li>Ensure portability, accuracy, and low latency for real-time interaction.</li></ul><br><b>Expected Outcomes</b><br><ul><li>Working prototype glove and software system.</li><li>Accurate sign-to-text/speech conversion (goal: &gt;90% accuracy).</li><li>Real-time visual feedback with gesture illustrations.</li><li>Mobile app/web interface for usability.</li></ul><br><b>Deliverables</b><br><ul><li>Functional prototype of the sensor glove</li><li>Working software application (web/mobile)</li><li>ML model with documentation</li><li>Codebase (GitHub/GitLab)</li><li>Video demo</li><li>Project report and presentation</li></ul></div>\n                               </td>\n                            </tr>\n\n                            <tr>\n                                <th>Organization</th>\n                            <td>Ministry of Social Justice &amp; Empowerment(MoSJE) </td>\n                                            \n                            </tr>  \n                            \n                            <tr>\n                                <th>Department</th>\n                            <td>\n                                Indian Sign Language Research &amp; Training Centre(ISLRTC) \n                                <!-- echo $user_info->department;  -->\n                            </td>\n                                            \n                            </tr>  \n\n                            <tr>\n                            <th>Category</th>\n                            <td>Hardware</td>\n                            </tr>\n\n                            <tr>\n                            <th>Theme</th>\n                            <td>Miscellaneous</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                              <th>Youtube Link</th>\n                              <td>\n                                    <a href=\" \" target=\"_blank\"> </a>\n                            </td>  \n                            </tr> \n                          <!--                             <tr>\n                              <th>Dataset Link</th>\n                              <td>\n                                \n                                    <br>\n                                     <a href=\"\"><br></a>\n                                 <a href=\"https://www.sih.gov.in/dataset/\"><br></a>\n                                                                                          </td>  \n                            </tr> -->\n                                                                <tr>\n                                    <th>Dataset Link</th>\n                                    <td>\n                                                                            </td>\n                                    </tr>\n\n                            <tr>\n                              <th>Contact info</th>\n                              <td>\n                                    <a href=\" \" target=\"_blank\"> </a>\n                            </td>  \n                            </tr> \n    \n                      </thead>\n                     </table>",
