    "organization": "Department of Science and Technology",
    "category": "Hardware",
    "description": "<table id=\"settings\" class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\">\n                        <thead>\n                        <tr>\n                            <th style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Problem Statement ID</th>\n                            <td>\n                                <div class=\"style-2\" style=\"overflow-y: auto; min-height:20px; max-height: 200px; width:100%;\"> 1546</div>\n                               </td>\n                            </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                            <th style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Problem Statement Title</th>\n                            <td>\n                                <div class=\"style-2\" style=\"overflow-y: auto; min-height:20px; max-height: 200px; width:100%;\"> Development of innovative design for flushing systems in western toilet sheets which can be used for deployment in public toilets.</div>\n                               </td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                            <th style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Description</th>\n                            <td>\n                                <div class=\"style-2\" style=\"overflow-y: auto; min-height:20px; max-height: 200px; width:100%;\"> Background: Public toilets are essential for maintaining hygiene in urban areas, but they often face challenges such as high usage, maintenance issues, and water wastage.\nDescription and Expected Solution: An innovative public toilet design is required so that maximum usable area gets cleans during the flushing and can be automated in a mechanized form (not electronic), so that after the usage, the flushing system gets activated automatically, and the whole usable area gets cleaned.</div>\n                               </td>\n                            </tr>\n\n                            <tr>\n                                <th>Organization</th>\n                            <td>Department of Science and Technology </td>\n                                            \n                            </tr>  \n                            \n                            <tr>\n                                <th>Department</th>\n                            <td>Department of Science and Technology </td>\n                                            \n                            </tr>  \n\n                            <tr>\n                            <th>Category</th>\n                            <td>Hardware</td>\n                            </tr>\n\n                            <tr>\n                            <th>Theme</th>\n                            <td>Miscellaneous</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                              <th>Youtube Link</th>\n                              <td>\n                                    <a href=\" \" target=\"_blank\"> </a>\n                            </td>  \n                            </tr> \n                                                      <tr>\n                              <th>Dataset Link</th>\n                              <td>\n                                <br>\n                                 <!-- <a href=\"https://www.sih.gov.in/uploads/psData/\"><br></a> -->\n                                                                                          </td>  \n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                              <th>Contact info</th>\n                              <td>\n                                    <a href=\" \" target=\"_blank\"> </a>\n                            </td>  \n                            </tr> \n    \n                      </thead>\n                     </table>",
